name: Puri Saron Hotel Madangan
address: Ds Madangan Petak Bitra, Petak Kaja, Kec. Gianyar, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80515, Indonesia
review 1: One of the best places I've ever visited, very quiet, comfortable, and relaxed, away from the crowds, the rooms are clean, good wifi, adult and children's swimming pools are free access, there are villas suitable for family gatherings or reunions. Large parking lot and suitable for retreats also.
review 2: Puri Saron Hotel in Madangan is a serene oasis nestled away from the city hustle, surrounded by lush greenery and tranquility. The peaceful environment offers a perfect escape for those seeking solace in nature. With its serene ambiance and picturesque surroundings, it’s an ideal retreat for rejuvenation and relaxation.
review 3: Good hotel, good service. Really secluded in Gianyar. Good place to stay if you have activities near Gianyar, there are lots of great waterfalls around.
review 4: Amazing place, kind staff and great value. The room is big nice, very chill and quiet and have a great atmosphere
review 5:
It’s ok location. Beautiful garden.
